::Stratus::

"If you don't mind, sir, I'll stick with this mode," Stratus says. He 
didn't know if he'd be accepted in his group with a mode like these 
bots had.

He exits the trailer when Motormaster comes to a complete stop, 
keeping his arms and legs inside the vehicle till such a time. 
Stratus looks around.

"What do we do now?"
